defaultWhat is the real evidence? The Public Law Project (PLP) have stated:
defaultOn the Today Programme on
default 23 April 2013, the Lord Chancellor was interviewed by John Humphreys about the Government’s plans to implement changes to judicial review procedure. The interview included the following exchange: 
defaultHumphreys: 
default“
defaultWhy are you doing it [making the changes]?
